  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_ratansi_arVol02Doc19.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>بمنّه تعالى</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>By the Grace of God</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="ara" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقر
               <persName ref="#mansour">منصور بن حميد النخلي</persName>
               ان عليه لسيت
               <persName ref="#ratansi">رطنسى بن برسوتم البانياني</persName>
              <lb/> خمسة و خمسين قرشا فضه افرنسياً مؤجلة عليه له الي مضي خمسة اشهر 
               <lb/>زمانا منذ اليوم وقد اثبت له بحقه هذا خمس نخلات مبسلى من ماله 
               <lb/>المسمى بستان جبيل الكاين ببلد 
               <placeName ref="#nakhl">نخل</placeName>
               اثباتا صحيحا ثابتا شرعا
               <lb/>اقرارا منه بذلك بتاريخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">يوم
               <num>٢٤</num>
               رمضان سنة
               <num>١٣١٤</num> 
              </date>
               وكتبه الفقير 
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#saleh">صالح بن عامر الطيواني</persName>
               بيده
               <lb/>اشهدني على ذلك فشهدت و انا الحقير 
               <persName ref="#hamidBSalem">حامد بن سالم بن محمد</persName>
               بيدي 
               <lb/>قذا خط القاضي 
               <persName ref="#saleh">صالح بن عامر</persName>
               صحيح و ثابت
               <gap/>
               الحقير
               <persName ref="#khalfan">خلفان بن عامر</persName>
               <gap/>
               تاريخ الورقة
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#mansour">Mansour bin Hamad Al-Nakhli</persName> acknowledges that he owes to the Seth <persName ref="#ratansi">Ratansi bin Purshottam Al-Banyani</persName>               
               <lb/><measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="55">fifty-five silver French <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qirsh</ref></measure>, delayed upon him for the duration of five months’
               <lb/>time from today, and he has confirmed for him [<persName ref="#ratansi">Ratansi</persName>] his [i.e. <persName ref="#ratansi">Ratansi's</persName>] right to five mature date palms from his [<persName ref="#mansour">Mansour's</persName>] property
               <lb/>which is called Jubail Garden in the town of <placeName ref="#nakhl">Nakhl[a]</placeName>, and this is a valid, legal confirmation
               <lb/>and an acknowledgement from him [<persName ref="#mansour">Mansour</persName>] of that, on the date of <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">24 Ramadan 1314</date>, and it was written by the wretched
               <lb/><persName ref="#saleh">Saleh bin Amer Al-Tiwani</persName>, in his own hand.
               <lb/>He had me bear witness to that, and I witnessed, and I am the wretched <persName ref="#hamidBSalem">Hamid bin Salem bin Mohammed</persName> 
               <lb/>This is the handwriting of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qazi">qadi</ref> <persName ref="#saleh">Saleh bin ‘Amer</persName>, confirmed and valid<gap/> <persName ref="#khalfan">Khalfan bin Amer</persName><gap/> on the date of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_waraqa">waraqa</ref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
